snippet.textDisplay:
The best song ever, Nazia and zoheb did. My parents knew their parents in Karachi, their house was tha 4th no and our was the first house of that lane in KDA karachi.We always met at Karachi Gymkhana all the times. When I hear this song , it reminds me those beautiful days, when Karachii was the best city of the world, I am 4 years older than Nazia  but my younger sister is same age as her, they were born in the same hospital Seventh Day in saddar area. I play this song hundred times it reminds me of those lovely days and when we were all so young.Still zoheb has the same voice and sweet personality, both brother sister were great kids and good human beings. I wish all the best forZoheb and Nazia to live in peace.
Sabina  canada
